* IPsec / IKE\nRoadmap\n(RFC 6071)
** Purpose
*** Map dozens of RFCs
*** Informational,\ndefines nothing
*** Obsoletes RFC 2411
*** Tags: S / E / B / I
** Core concepts
*** SA (one-way)
*** SPI
*** SPD / SAD / PAD
*** Transport vs tunnel
** Seven doc groups
*** Architecture
*** ESP / AH
*** Encryption alg
*** Combined alg
*** Integ-protection alg
*** IKE
** Versions
*** IPsec-v2 -> v3
*** IKEv1 -> IKEv2
*** IKE SA vs IPsec SA\n(CHILD_SA)
** Extensions
*** NAT traversal
*** ESN
*** PKI4IPsec
*** Dead peer detection
*** MOBIKE / remote access
** Crypto algorithms
*** IANA value + RFC
*** Levels MUST..MAY\n(SHOULD+ / MUST-)
*** DES deprecated
** Reach beyond IPsec
*** Outgrowths\n(policy, MIB, IPComp,\nBTNS, KINK, IPSECKEY)
*** Protocols using IPsec\n(MIP, OSPF, HIP, BGP, SIP)
*** Protocols adapting IKE\n(EAP, Fibre Channel)
@endmindmap
